<li id="cite_note-225"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-225">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFPoliak2005" class="citation book cs1">Poliak, A. N. (2005) [1942]. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=YVGdl09xAp4C&amp;pg=PA27">"The Influence of C̱ẖingiz-Ḵẖān's Yāsa upon the General Organization of the Mamlūk State"</a>. In Hawting, Gerald R. (ed.). <i>Muslims, Mongols, and Crusaders: An Anthology of Articles Published in the "Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies"</i>. Vol.&#160;10. <a href="/wiki/London" title="London">London</a> and <a href="/wiki/New_York_City" title="New York City">New York</a>: <a href="/wiki/Routledge" title="Routledge">Routledge</a>. pp.&#160;27–41. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1017%2FS0041977X0009008X">10.1017/S0041977X0009008X</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-7007-1393-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-7007-1393-6"><bdi>978-0-7007-1393-6</bdi></a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/609130">609130</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:155480831">155480831</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+Influence+of+C%CC%B1%E1%BA%96ingiz-%E1%B8%B4%E1%BA%96%C4%81n%27s+Y%C4%81sa+upon+the+General+Organization+of+the+Maml%C5%ABk+State&amp;rft.btitle=Muslims%2C+Mongols%2C+and+Crusaders%3A+An+Anthology+of+Articles+Published+in+the+%22Bulletin+of